<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244133>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43A–I. Hexapopha itabaiana sp. nov., male, SEM images (IBSP 68163; PBI_OON 52568). A–B carapace. A lateral view. B ventral view. C mouthparts, ventral view. D–E endites. D ventral view. E detail of D, showing projections. F abdomen, lateral view. G sperm pore, ventral view. H right palp, retrolateral view. I embolus, retrolateral view. Abbreviations: c, conductor; mp, median projection; P, projection." ;
